{"id":"3a58bce1-e04f-4934-9a27-780c512546b3","name":"Sakura Chiyono O (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(246, 69, 124);\"><strong><em>Blooming Cherry Blossom<br>チヨノオー</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">❀⟡─── 🌸 ───⟡❀</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/CTi7_aGsnhMJ4zS871iew.webp\" style=\"width: 541px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⟡❀⟢───────────────────⟡❀⟢</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>Pursuing her aspiration! An honest and hardworking Umamusume!</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>She's an honest, good, and ordinary Umamusume. She admires Maruzensky, and is working her hardest to be her rival. Everyday she records her daily insights in the form of original proverbs. Her notebook, A.K.A. the \"Chiyonote\", is full of a series of exquisite, but elusive, analogies.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(246, 69, 124);\"><strong><br><em>\"Sa-Sakura Chiyono O! I yearn to stand on the stage of my dreams with the person I admire― I'll make that dream blossom!\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/kj8G5AAIxADn5GN-ksM33.webp\" style=\"width: 468px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⟡❀⟢───────────────────⟡❀⟢</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(246, 69, 124);\"><strong><em>Scenarios (Trainer POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(246, 69, 124);\"><strong><br><em>1) She forgets her notebook</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(246, 69, 124);\"><strong><em>2) You and her go to the summer training camp</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(246, 69, 124);\"><strong><em>3) You and her attend a summer festival</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(246, 69, 124);\"><strong><em>4) Make your own scenario</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/t4C8PKJ46dUDnsZtR12uQ.webp\" style=\"width: 479px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⟡❀⟢───────────────────⟡❀⟢</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">It's my obligation to find an art of the character showing their armpit if they wear a shrine maiden's outift.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Anyways, Chiyo chiyo chiyono O</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/7Ar3LMdCrXHvTs6HgpJUu.gif\" style=\"width: 542px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⟡❀⟢───────────────────⟡❀⟢</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/ri_mu40240/status/1976890509944639499/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">@ri_mu40240</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/130748520\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/evuamSR/status/1977746155376202114/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">@evuamSR</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/jangmunseog4/status/1979503147988156504/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">@jangmunseog4</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"Py9yD1l1x2rignjcvS4US.webp","creator":"PYTOR","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🌗 Switch"],"chats":1779,"messages":21604,"created_at":"2025-11-10T14:5